channel.description: PrOgReSziVe FiLiPiNaS or "Progressive Philippines" is a YouTube Channel that showcases the Philippines and the Filipino people. It promotes the diverse beauty of the country, the multifaceted culture of its people and the dedication of the true patriots and noble Filipinos and their quest to see the motherland fulfill it dreams to be a prosperous nation and a beacon of democracy and freedom in the Pacific. Please help us achieve these goals. Thanks for visiting our channel and Mabuhay!
